Maintainer: Kyle Caudle <kyle.caudle@sdsmt.edu>
Description: A set of tools for basic tensor operators.  A tensor in
        the context of data analysis in a multidimensional array. The
        tools in this package rely on using any discrete transformation
        (e.g. Fast Fourier Transform (FFT)).  Standard tools included
        are the Eigenvalue decomposition of a tensor, the QR
        decomposition and LU decomposition.  Other functionality
        includes the inverse of a tensor and the transpose of a
        symmetric tensor. Functionality in the package is outlined in
        Kernfeld, E., Kilmer, M., and Aeron, S. (2015)
        <doi:10.1016/j.laa.2015.07.021>.
